Episode Hub is a free story-reading platform powered by rewarded and banner ads. Users unlock episodes by watching ads, and the platform features a user-friendly interface for reading and discovering new stories.
Key Features
User Authentication: Sign in with email, Google, or anonymously
Unlock Episodes: Watch rewarded ads to unlock new episodes
Immersive Reading: Read episodes with a clean and intuitive interface
Tracking Progress: Track reading progress and bookmark stories
Rating System: Rate stories after reading
Tech Stack
Frontend: Next.js for a fast and scalable user interface
Backend: Firebase for authentication, data storage, and ad integration
Database: Firestore for storing user data and story content


